<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Review Has a New Reply</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..12,200..1000;1,6..12,200..1000&family=Nunito:ital,wght@0,200..1000;1,200..1000&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            font-family: "Nunito", sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #51545e;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b6e76;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>New Reply to Your Review!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello <%= fullname %>,</p>
            <p>Someone has replied to your review on "<strong><%= courseName %></strong>".</p>
            <p>Your Review: <strong>"<%= reviewComment %>"</strong></p>
            <p>Reply: <strong>"<%= replyComment %>"</strong></p>
            <p>We encourage you to check it out and continue the conversation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 HTU LMS. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
